    <section_number>87</section_number>
    <catch_line>Limitation Upon Tax Exemption</catch_line>
    <order_by>87</order_by>
    <text>
        Land, outside the location of the railroad five rods in width, taken or purchased for railroad, depot or station purposes shall not be exempt from taxation.
    </text>
